		<td><b>New directory structure for WIki pages</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've changed the page structure for the <a href="http://nesdevwiki.org" class="postlink">wiki</a> to be a little cleaner.
<br />
<br />Instead of pages being at nesdevwiki.org/index.php/Foo, they will be at nesdevwiki.org/wiki/Foo. This matches the Wikipedia structure, and will be a little nicer to link or type.
<br />
<br />I left a redirect for the old structure, so existing links should still work. Let me know if you find anything broken, or find some old links that don't work anymore.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


